{"tid":2022686,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪比亞路腎結石留醫","createTime":"2020-05-18T12:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T10:11:39.000Z","uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"94460425db1fba11bb08e84fd9225af5e18c142e","tid":2022686,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】前意大利金童迪比亞路因為腎結石，在洛杉磯的醫院留醫。<br />\n前祖雲達斯球星迪比亞路（Alessandro Del Piero）透過社交網絡，展示一張他戴上口罩在UCLA醫院留醫的照片，圖說是「我仍然不能相信，只有3毫米的一些東西可以造成如此傷害。」 看到這模樣難免令球迷擔心，不過他很快表明是預防勝於治療，相信問題不大。 曾協助意大利贏得2006年世界盃冠軍的迪比亞路，於2015年正式宣佈高掛球靴，他為祖雲達斯上陣超過700場，射入290球，他不時留意球壇動向，特別留意母會斑馬兵團，寄語球員永遠沒有免費午餐，「這是我的經驗之談，沒有人會無條件給你些甚麼，你在每一場比賽都要證明自己。」<br />\n<br />\n腎結石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35267019b5c45bb9217b68f12530e19e65b1dfbd","tid":2022686,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"腎結石真係害人不賤"},{"pid":"f2454cff6d4c6a3f20ae80df30e5eda342e99855","tid":2022686,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"腎結石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf59ae3a8be7e7e664edc153dd3fe3c5ef5b0283","tid":2022686,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2454cff6d4c6a3f20ae80df30e5eda342e99855","tid":2022686,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T13:35:06.000Z","msg":"腎結石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:28:13.000Z","msg":"呢個po唔會一頁"},{"pid":"298f985fe7bf8732f2f99c7c1dd76e54f47e2cba","tid":2022686,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":